          for immediate results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <%# Feature 1 %>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div
              class="
                flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex
                items-center justify-center text-accent font-bold text-xl
              "
            >
              1
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">
                Upload Your Photo
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Start by uploading a real photo of your garden. We handle the
                perspective settings automatically.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%# Feature 2 %>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div
              class="
                flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex
                items-center justify-center text-accent font-bold text-xl
              "
            >
              2
            </div>
