                Smart Brush Tool
              </h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Our interactive tour shows you how to paint over areas to
                redesign (like grass or fences) with precision.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%# Feature 3 %>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div
              class="
                flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex
                items-center justify-center text-accent font-bold text-xl
              "
            >
              3
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Style Selection</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Choose your preferred aesthetic from curated design styles like
                Modern, Japanese, or Xeriscape.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%# Feature 4 %>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div
              class="
                flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex
                items-center justify-center text-accent font-bold text-xl
              "
            >
              4
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">AI Refinement</h3>
              <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
                Learn to use the AI Editor to request specific changes (e.g.,
                "add a stone path") using natural language.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-accent/5 rounded-3xl transform rotate-2"></div>

